data.description: Don\'t miss this lovely home at the end of a cul-de-sac street that has customized features. Granite counter tops with stainless appliances in the kitchen. All new kitchen cabinets. Brick accented fireplace in large family room with lots of natural lighting. Located in desirable Clear Creek ISD and zoned to Clear Lake High School.

responsivePhotos.caption: Beautiful rich new cabinets through out kitchen with upgraded granite counter tops.
Lovely two story home on quite cul-de-sac.
Large yard plenty of room to grow, play and have a pool!
Kitchen has lovely stainless steel appliances.
This kitchen has a large window over looking the back yard. This kitchen also features an undermounted stainless steel sink, designer lighting and wine rack.
Light, bright and open breakfast area.
Spacious entrance area for decorating opportunities.
This formal dining area has room for large table and hutch.
Breakfast area has easy access to family room and outside
Family room has natural lighting, a cozy fireplace as well as recess lighting.
The master bedroom has two closets
Oversized back porch ready for weekend barbecues and entertaining
Plenty of room for all your outdoor activities
